    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you choose this domain at 1st level, you learn two languages of your choice. You also become proficient in your choice of two of the following skills: Arcana, History, Nature, or Religion; and can use your Wisdom modifier in place of your Intelligence modifier with the chosen skills.</p><p>Your proficiency bonus is doubled for any ability check you make that uses either of those skills.</p><blockquote><p><strong>When you get this feature, if you wish to use your Wisdom modifier in place of your Intelligence modifier for the chosen skills, you will need to change it manually on your character sheet.</strong></p></blockquote>",
